# Codegen example apps regenerate `grid.bin`, `pdemodel.txt`, `datain/`,
# `dataout/`, and companion bins (xdg/udg/vdg/wdg/partition) via
# `bash regenerate.sh`. Don't commit them — some are megabytes (cone's
# grid.bin alone is ~4 MB).
*_codegen/grid.bin
*_codegen/datain/
*_codegen/dataout/
*_codegen/pdemodel.txt
*_codegen/xdg.bin
*_codegen/udg.bin
*_codegen/vdg.bin
*_codegen/wdg.bin
*_codegen/partition.bin
